{"tid":1391560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[解毒] 乜野係獨立調查委員會? 唔好俾人誤導!!","createTime":"2019-07-31T13:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:17:51.000Z","uid":218313,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"217c0e008fa751283fa0928aeaca9ac99018ebb6","tid":1391560,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"五大訴求每個巴打都好清楚<br />\n其中<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立調查委員會</span></strong>呢排係講得最多最多!<br />\n<br />\n但依家我覺得巴打們係人云亦云, 你地究竟有無理解過, 個委員會係乜東東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以我<span style=\"color: blue;\">個人理解</span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(有錯請屌)</span></span>, 獨立調查委員會係由一班<span style=\"color: green;\">獨立於監警會既公正人仕 (例如: 法官)</span><br />\n去調查由612 開始發生既警權失當事宜<br />\n<br />\n我理解, 如果日後真係有可能成立的話, 呢個委員會只不過係為調查<span style=\"color: red;\">單一事件</span>而成立<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而並不是恒常可以抗衡警權既組職!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然依家係好長遠, 但如果日後, 又發生重大爭議時<br />\n呢個委員會仲存唔存在??<br />\n<br />\n我地要既係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獨立既警監會</span></span>, 我地要既唔係自己人查自己人既垃圾警監會!!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無左呢樣野, 香港只會繼續發生警權無間地獄, 永不返生!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無把打再補充一下?"},{"pid":"c94c3f4f90f66a8531bff0954d57419960b7e605","tid":1391560,"uid":172596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:08:54.000Z","msg":"早排我聽到某法官話示威者其實收美國佬錢<br />\n佢地係離地到大家無法想像的"},{"pid":"8137272928da909c7bf1336d6017db61f50bb04d","tid":1391560,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c94c3f4f90f66a8531bff0954d57419960b7e605","tid":1391560,"uid":172596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:08:54.000Z","msg":"早排我聽到某法官話示威者其實收美國佬錢<br />\n佢地係離地到大家無法想像的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:12:17.000Z","msg":"法官都係人, 堅係有偏黃偏藍情況出現<br />\n我地行既係法治, 係制度<br />\n制度就係盡量將所為&quot;人為因素&quot; 減到最低"},{"pid":"fe788581e74fd77916714e28a63f423ce4b98596","tid":1391560,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:18:13.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"840556788a1683ecdc9986f8d00c20058a76d57c","tid":1391560,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:21:39.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"e2e1704d85883e6a26aa67278356564d16bacb4d","tid":1391560,"uid":64938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:22:08.000Z","msg":"[香城online]傳令兵的技巧和心得<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n就快又發夢啦，手足幫手廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd117a1d84ce162e2646a7e30f632c20330ab28d","tid":1391560,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"de731cb4eae5bff794e612a17633a0655c4778db","tid":1391560,"uid":196430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:26:34.000Z","msg":"推，事態早已經超出獨立調查可以處理嘅範圍"},{"pid":"74bfee40bc8f2c887bb307c6ae8822057764b0bf","tid":1391560,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:30:07.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"c74e73f05a0b59a1f332953e5714c9aa21cd77fa","tid":1391560,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"651be61cee879c2fb33a9d5d10643343bdfc9bc0","tid":1391560,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13